1
00:00:36,119 --> 00:00:37,320
Haiyang, apologize.

2
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:38,880
I'm sorry.

3
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:40,560
Fine.

4
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:41,960
Then you compensate me now...

5
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:43,240
at the market price.

6
00:00:43,439 --> 00:00:44,200
You can't afford it.

7
00:00:44,359 --> 00:00:45,200
Then all of you pay.

8
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,359
Wang Yingrong.

9
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:48,039
Don't go too far.

10
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,640
We already apologized to you.

11
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:50,799
And you still want us to pay?

12
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:51,920
You're crossing the line.

13
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,280
Am I crossing the line?

14
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:54,640
Zheng Haiyang said it himself.

15
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:55,679
He slaughtered my pigs.

16
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:56,719
Why shouldn't he pay?

17
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:57,920
Your family ruined...

18
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:58,960
my son's wedding.

19
00:00:59,159 --> 00:00:59,880
Why shouldn't you pay?

20
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,240
You...

21
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,439
Pay us back the betrothal money first.

22
00:01:01,479 --> 00:01:02,119
Wang Yingrong.

23
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,200
Your losses...

24
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,040
I'll figure out a way.

25
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,439
Yes, Sister Yingrong.

26
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:08,200
If you keep making a scene...

27
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,040
it won't be good for anyone.

28
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,000
You leave first.

29
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:10,799
Leave first.

30
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:11,480
I haven't finished speaking.

31
00:01:11,719 --> 00:01:12,319
Calm down.

32
00:01:12,319 --> 00:01:13,000
Don't push me.

33
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:13,760
Go, go, go.

34
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:34,879
Zheng Xiaochuan.

35
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:37,239
Chen Xuelin, pay for my pigs.

36
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:39,439
Chen Xuelin, pay for my pigs.

37
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:42,239
Chen Xuelin, pay for my pigs.

38
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,120
Chen Xuelin, pay up.

39
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:43,719
You shrew.

40
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,280
What are you making a scene here for?

41
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:46,959
Pay for my pigs.

42
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,120
Your son...

43
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,200
slaughtered two of my pigs.

44
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:50,159
The neighbors can testify.

45
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:52,040
Your kid Haiyang...

46
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,200
killed someone else's pigs.

47
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,480
He really should pay.

48
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,959
None of your business.

49
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:58,719
Chen Xuelin's family slaughtered her pigs.

50
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,359
You were suspended by the factory.

51
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,799
You still have the face to come back and make a scene?

52
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:04,599
Isn't it just raising pigs?

53
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,000
If I were you...

54
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,799
I wouldn't dare come back to this factory.

55
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:08,879
Disgraceful.

56
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,080
So shameful.

57
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,479
If it were anyone else...

58
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,520
they'd hide when seeing their coworkers.

59
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:14,719
Exactly.

60
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,840
So ambitious...

61
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,000
doing well out there...

62
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,400
show everyone then.

63
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,120
Still thought...

64
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,599
you could do something big.

65
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,879
Turns out it's just raising pigs.

66
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:23,159
And the pigs got slaughtered.

67
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,879
I may not be doing well...

68
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:26,840
but I earn money with my own two hands.

69
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:29,080
Your family is just looking for trouble.

70
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,319
One tricked me into raising pigs...

71
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,520
one slaughtered my pigs...

72
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:33,439
and another crashed my motorcycle.

73
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:35,120
You have to pay for my motorcycle too.

74
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,120
What will you do if we don't pay?

75
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,280
I have nothing to lose now.

76
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,520
I'll follow you wherever you go.

77
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,520
If you don't pay for my pigs...

78
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,800
I'll pester you to the end.

79
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,240
Chen Xuelin, pay for my pigs.

80
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,759
Chen Xuelin, pay for my pigs.

81
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:48,360
Chen Xuelin, pay for my pigs.

82
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,080
Chen Xuelin, pay for my pigs.

83
00:02:50,319 --> 00:02:51,159
Chen Xuelin!

84
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,120
Pay for my pigs!

85
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,439
Pay for my pigs!

86
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,039
You leech.

87
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,719
Come and take this evil neighbor away.

88
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:02,280
If it's not raising pigs stinking people to death...

89
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,400
it's her hounding people to death for debt.

90
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:06,159
Everyone come look...

91
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:07,879
at this shrew.

92
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,680
Make way.

93
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,840
She, this shrew...

94
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:10,680
Mom.

95
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,800
Bullying people.

96
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,199
Minjiang, you're here.

97
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,000
Wang Yingrong.

98
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,319
Let's talk.

99
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,599
Look, she's really fierce.

100
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,560
Mom.

101
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,199
I have three sons.

102
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:39,360
Am I afraid of a Shrew like you?

103
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,000
Speak up.

104
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,759
Do you have money for me or what?

105
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:49,159
Not right now.

106
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:50,800
But I'll figure something out.

107
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,599
I knew you were useless.

108
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,680
You can't say that.

109
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,919
I truly want to solve the problem.

110
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,000
Did I say something wrong?

111
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:01,400
Don't you know what your brother did?

112
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,520
Don't you know how excessive your mom is?

113
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:06,439
I have nothing left now.

114
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,800
Is it wrong for me to ask for it back?

115
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,240
From what you're saying...

116
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,479
It seems I can't pay it off.

117
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:13,159
Then I'll give myself to you.

118
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:13,879
How about that?

119
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,399
Who wants you to offer yourself up?

120
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,040
You're out of your mind.

121
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:23,519
That's not what I meant.

122
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,560
I mean...

123
00:04:24,879 --> 00:04:25,839
I'll be your collateral.

124
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:27,720
If you need help with anything in the future...

125
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,439
Just tell me.

126
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,240
I can definitely help.

127
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,519
Your motorcycle...

128
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:31,800
Leave it to me.

129
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,480
Do you enjoy tricking me?

130
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:35,199
Say something practical.

131
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,319
How is it not practical?

132
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:39,279
The factory recording...

133
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,079
Who recorded it for you?

134
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,360
And who played it for you?

135
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,079
And...

136
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,600
Is that not practical enough?

137
00:04:44,199 --> 00:04:44,480
You...

138
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,079
Why bring this up now?

139
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,079
Let me tell you...

140
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,439
Let's keep things separate.

141
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:51,879
You must compensate me for that pig.

142
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,920
I got it.

143
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,439
My dear lady, if you could just give me more time...

144
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,680
I'd be eternally grateful.

145
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,079
So, are we...

146
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,600
Agreed then?

147
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,000
Who agreed with you?

148
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,600
Full of yourself.

149
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:09,000
Your pig is gone.

150
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:10,680
What's the plan now?

151
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:12,800
I keep my word.

152
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,759
If you need help with anything later...

153
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:15,360
Just say the word.

154
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,560
You should look after yourself first.

155
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:19,240
You haven't even figured out your own issues.

156
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,319
And you want to help others.

157
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,879
You really are something.

158
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:30,199
Sis.

159
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,319
Yingrong.

160
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:37,920
Sis.

161
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:39,319
What's wrong?

162
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:44,480
Here.

163
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,279
Give Bao'er to me.

164
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:49,439
Let's go.

165
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,240
Let's go home.

166
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:51,920
Be careful.

167
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:57,920
Sis, be careful.

168
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,560
Sis

169
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,360
Here

170
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,800
Your blood sugar is low

171
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,639
Sit down first

172
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,120
I'll go mix some brown sugar water for you

173
00:06:24,519 --> 00:06:25,120
Look at you

174
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,000
You look half-dead

175
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:28,199
What are you sitting here for?

176
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,879
My grandson has eczema on his bottom

177
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:33,839
In a bit

178
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:35,079
wipe him down well

179
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,079
Also

180
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,160
take that basin of clothes and...

181
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,879
I say, Auntie

182
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,480
my sister needs to rest right now

183
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,480
Besides

184
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,720
whoever brought that child home

185
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,720
should take care of him

186
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,360
Is that how you speak to your elders?

187
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:48,720
Our Li family

188
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,879
without this grandson

189
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,240
would have no descendants

190
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,439
Mom

191
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:55,079
Guangming and I are still young

192
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,680
We can still have more

193
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,160
Have more?

194
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:58,279
You'll give birth to maggots

195
00:06:58,399 --> 00:06:59,759
I went to the health clinic today

196
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:01,399
The doctor told me

197
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,199
that from now on

198
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:04,040
you can never have children again

199
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:05,519
You barren hen

200
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,480
Our family

201
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,000
feeds you well and keeps you

202
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,959
yet you let your family

203
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,560
come here screaming and shouting

204
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,000
I...

205
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:14,199
What did you say?

206
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:14,920
I...

207
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,839
Why can't I have children anymore?

208
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,519
Raise him yourself

209
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,439
Don't come bothering my sister

210
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,800
A barren hen

211
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,000
Yingrong

212
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,959
Do you know something?

213
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,360
Tell me the truth

214
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,759
What is actually wrong with my body?

215
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,319
Why can't I give birth anymore?

216
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,279
Sis

217
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:46,279
You were sent to the hospital too late that day

218
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,399
Difficult labor caused massive bleeding

219
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:51,560
They had to remove your uterus

220
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:53,759
I...

221
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,199
Mom and I didn't mean to hide it from you

222
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:58,720
We just didn't know how to tell you

223
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,000
It's all fate

224
00:08:22,399 --> 00:08:22,920
Sis

225
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:24,800
Let's leave the Li family

226
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,519
Let's go back

227
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,639
Family harmony brings prosperity

228
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,600
I've thought about it a lot

229
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,840
We women

230
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,840
in this society

231
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:43,919
compared to men

232
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,240
have a much harder life

233
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:49,200
In the end, we

234
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,879
have to rely on them

235
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,600
No, Sis

236
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,679
Life is our own

237
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:57,679
We can only rely on ourselves

238
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,600
Our family

239
00:08:59,759 --> 00:09:01,480
will support and protect you

240
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,480
You're not having an easy time right now either

241
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:07,720
If I go back, I'll just add to your burden

242
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:11,639
Besides, Mom wouldn't let me come back

243
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:13,240
Sis

244
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,639
It's okay, Sis

245
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:22,159
Sis

246
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,960
Don't cry

247
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,480
A woman's life

248
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:37,919
doesn't have to depend on a man to be good

249
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:40,399
Big Sister married the wrong man

250
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:42,720
Her whole life has been wasted

251
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:44,159
I, Wang Yingrong

252
00:09:44,559 --> 00:09:47,159
am going to make a name for myself

253
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,320
Yingrong

254
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,440
Since you're at our shop entrance,

255
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,639
why not come in and sit?

256
00:09:58,799 --> 00:09:59,600
Uncle Fang

257
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,440
Come, quick.

258
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,720
Go in. Sit inside.

259
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:03,799
Sit inside.

260
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:06,399
I heard

261
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,960
you raised pigs for a while.

262
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,399
If you want to sell,

263
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,360
you can bring them to our shop anytime.

264
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,360
Uncle Fang

265
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,120
I'm not raising them anymore.

266
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,000
What happened?

267
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:18,879
Raising pigs depends on the site.

268
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:20,679
I thought it was too simple.

269
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:24,320
Every bottle of good wine

270
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:25,639
requires

271
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:27,919
repeated blending and testing.

272
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:29,240
Only with the right proportions

273
00:10:29,799 --> 00:10:31,320
can the taste be mellow.

274
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,360
Doing business

275
00:10:33,919 --> 00:10:35,279
is just like making wine.

276
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,120
It's the same principle.

277
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,679
But I still have high hopes for you.

278
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,120
You have drive.

279
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,720
Thank you, Uncle Fang.

280
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,679
Here comes the signature dish!

281
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:43,440
Sweet and Sour Chicken.

282
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:45,840
This is our shop's signature dish,

283
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,519
Sweet and Sour Chicken.

284
00:10:46,519 --> 00:10:47,399
Come, have a taste.

285
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:48,519
Boss Fang,

286
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:50,799
this Sweet and Sour Chicken is really tasty.

287
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,279
Is there a secret recipe?

288
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,320
What secret recipe?

289
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,720
It's just home-style cooking.

290
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,840
But the vinegar I use

291
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:01,120
is the old vinegar from the Xu family factory.

292
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,039
Baliang Vinegar.

293
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:05,120
You know it too.

294
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,639
My second aunt brewed that.

295
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:08,440
Then,

296
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:10,320
can you help me contact her?

297
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,679
I want to buy some more.

298
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:14,919
Something happened at my second aunt's home.

299
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,480
She probably can't brew anymore.

300
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:20,120
However,

301
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,480
I still have some at home.

302
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,200
My second aunt left some for us.

303
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,519
I'll bring it over to you in a couple of days.

304
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,600
That's great.

305
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:29,080
So Baliang Vinegar is this popular.

306
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,399
Do you want it?

307
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:33,399
Play this one.

308
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,039
I'll take it.

309
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:34,960
Hurry up with this.

310
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:39,759
Boss Tang,

311
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:40,639
the person you're looking for

312
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:41,919
is right in this workshop.

313
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,480
Excuse me,

314
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,039
which one is Master Zheng?

315
00:11:47,279 --> 00:11:48,080
Zheng Minjiang?

316
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:51,720
I'm the workshop director, his boss.

317
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,919
You can tell me what you need.

318
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:55,759
The province recommended I find Master Zheng

319
00:11:55,759 --> 00:11:57,000
to help me debug some machines.

320
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,039
It's very urgent.

321
00:11:58,039 --> 00:11:59,799
I'd like to ask Master Zheng for help.

322
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,480
Let's go.

323
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:04,679
As long as he gets the machine running,

324
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,840
I'll pay by the day.

325
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:06,799
Every day,

326
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,039
two hundred yuan.

327
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:09,840
Just one day

328
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,440
equals two or three months of our wages!

329
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:13,080
Where did this big boss come from?

330
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:15,679
Zheng Minjiang...

331
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,639
isn't in the factory.

332
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:19,799
Debugging machines, right?

333
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:20,679
I can do that too.

334
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,240
I happen to be free.

335
00:12:22,879 --> 00:12:23,519
Give me the toolbox.

336
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,279
I'll go with you.

337
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,919
I'm looking for Master Zheng.

338
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,320
That Master Zheng isn't even a director.

339
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,440
The man standing before you

340
00:12:32,639 --> 00:12:34,159
is our workshop's Director Li.

341
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,600
Surely a director is better than a regular worker.

342
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,519
You really don't recognize a true expert.

343
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:40,600
I'm extremely busy myself,

344
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:42,080
making time to help you out.

345
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,000
If you're going to be picky,

346
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,440
then go back where you came from.

347
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:46,799
Well then...

348
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:48,200
I'll have to trouble you, Director Li.

349
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:49,679
My car is at the factory gate.

350
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,000
After you, after you.

351
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:54,639
Let me tell you,

352
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:56,279
this guy drove here in a sedan.

353
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,519
He must be a big boss.

354
00:12:57,799 --> 00:12:58,360
Director Li...

355
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,399
has hit the jackpot this time.
